{"tid":807301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【甲醛小學】入課室即嘔！家長揭指數超標 開學日近千學生請病假","createTime":"2018-09-05T11:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T15:42:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"716dc20569de59ae8f42c2f6f3aa6b550f4ef990","tid":807301,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536140071_aa37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536140071_aa37.jpg&h=71c5e58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深圳南油小學開學日有近千學生請病假。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536140072_cf00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536140072_cf00.png&h=386a163b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內媒走訪發現，涉事小學教室內擺放多株植物，桌子旁掛着茶包。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有內地男子因為租住了「甲醛屋」，患上白血病身亡。深圳南油小學新裝修落成，周一（3日）開學日當日有近千名學生集體缺席，其中10多個班級缺席率超過80%。有家長反映，子女疑因學校甲醛嚴重超標，不適嘔吐，決定將孩子留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n位於深圳南山區核心地帶的南油小學是一所全日制公營學校，創辦於1986年，為廣東省一級學校，該校目前共有42班，161名教職員工，1,976名學生。校方於2015年8月啟動原址重建工作，1,600多名學生被暫時安置到另一間學校上學，3年新校舍落成，於本年度新學期使用。<br />\n<br />\n南山區南油小學有部份家長反映，子女在課室報到時出現身體不適、喉嚨不適，甚至嘔吐。有家長自行測試教室甲醛濃度，結果發現超標，便不敢讓孩子上學。可是，南山區教育局回應，學校開學前已請權威專業機構檢測過兩次甲醛濃度，檢測結果均為合格，稱學校環境指標不存在問題，學校具備開學條件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180905/58647632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180905%2F58647632&d=MWJ%2FoQsH6fUX2op4UrBM2gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=72553c1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180905%2F58647632&h=2b5be26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180905/58647632</a>"},{"pid":"7e75b6749ceff4394d384f1d387cf5fc07e8de79","tid":807301,"uid":101110,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"遲早到香港"},{"pid":"9808dd16d56f5a64915efb8287bf46b9a842f20c","tid":807301,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"權威專業機構 <br />\n公司名黎？"},{"pid":"39cccf9a382a27976b91f45de07b183fff0eb5bc","tid":807301,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"《支那榮耀》"},{"pid":"593c7cbfb29a6c96fe06709111a46ba84d70d2d9","tid":807301,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"從小訓練百毒不侵"},{"pid":"023f8b04468d2ea3f3c2360f0e1b5d390b9c6827","tid":807301,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:55:48.000Z","msg":"檢測結果均為合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73fb2a0ab34d259ed5a9c3d222b25d48065734e","tid":807301,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"不存在問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813504754a17cdf8b7a645897157ac85f0a98660","tid":807301,"uid":60281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"去大灣區讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc0a82b05788c1f8ac996fa623ff3ef0fb18ee1","tid":807301,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6300ef6e599e217c5c9fc8317f5467762403c9f3","tid":807301,"uid":153239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"023f8b04468d2ea3f3c2360f0e1b5d390b9c6827","tid":807301,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:55